LEFT: Wield an item in your left hand

Syntax: left <item>
        left nothing

DESCRIPTION:
  Wields the specified item in your left hand (off-hand). Useful for
  holding a pistol, shield, or secondary weapon while your right hand
  holds a primary weapon.

  left nothing : clears the left hand

EXAMPLE:
  left cp40 laser

SEE ALSO: right, wield, unwield, weapons
